Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.33,0:05:12.71,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}我独自在黑暗中流浪
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.71,0:05:17.42,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}前进前进  循着孤独的丝线
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.04,0:05:25.35,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}只为将你我紧紧相连
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.58,0:05:30.36,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}将那些深埋心底  压抑已久的呐喊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.06,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}全都宣泄出来
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.48,0:05:38.21,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}只凭一次明灭闪烁  就将束缚抛弃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.40,0:05:43.03,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}只需一道苍蓝彗尾  便将长夜洞穿
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.03,0:05:48.45,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}独属于你的生命  你选择怎样活着
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.80,0:05:52.96,Insert - CN - 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}让那刹那的悸动  响彻吧闪耀吧
Comment: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:15.40,Note,,0,0,0,,Half & Half
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:41.49,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}ねえ　この気持ち何だっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.06,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}届く方を知って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:47.48,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}本当は分かってる　なぜなら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.91,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}単純明快で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.77,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}少女漫画のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:58.07,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}キラキラしてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:05.74,Insert - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}自信とか　根拠とかは無くてもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.21,0:06:41.49,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}我说  这种心情究竟为何
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.06,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}我已明了这份心意该传递给谁
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.06,0:06:47.48,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}其实我明白的  因为这份心意
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.91,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}简单又明了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.03,0:06:53.77,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}就像少女漫画那样
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.95,0:06:58.07,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}只要能一直闪闪发光
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.11,0:07:05.74,Insert - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H00&}就算没有自信  没有依据也无妨
